English: <color=red>WARNING: Emergency power supply unit failed. Requires a manual restart at a terminal in: </color> <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: <color=red>AVERTISSEMENT : échec du lancement de l'unité d'alimentation de secours. Redémarrage manuel requis depuis un terminal de la</color> <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

Italian.Translation: <color=red>ATTENZIONE: alimentatore di emergenza guasto. Richiesto riavvio manuale su un terminale in: </color> <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

German.Translation: <color=red>WARNUNG: Notstromversorgungseinheit ausgefallen. Manueller Neustart an einem Terminal in</color> <color=orange>ZONE 183</color> erforderlich.

Spanish.Translation: <color=red>ADVERTENCIA: Fallo en la unidad eléctrica de apoyo. Debe reiniciarse manualmente en un terminal de la </color> <color=orange>ZONE 183</color>.

Russian.Translation: <color=red>ВНИМАНИЕ! Ошибка аварийного источника питания. Требуется ручная перезагрузка на терминале в</color> <color=orange>ZONE 183</color>.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: <color=red>AVISO: Falha na unidade de fornecimento elétrico de emergência. Reinício manual necessário em um terminal em: </color> <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>.

Polish.Translation: <color=red>OSTRZEŻENIE: usterka awaryjnej jednostki zasilającej. Wymagane ponowne ręczne uruchomienie z terminalu w </color><color=orange>strefie 183 [ZONE_183].</color>

Japanese.Translation: <color=red>警告：緊急電力供給ユニット作動失敗。以下のゾーンの端末での手動再起動が必要：</color><color=orange>ZONE 183</color>

Korean.Translation: <color=red>경고: 비상 파워 서플라이 유닛 고장. </color> <color=orange>ZONE 183</color> 터미널에서 수동 재시작 필요

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: <color=red>警告：緊急電源裝置發生故障。需要在以下終端手動重啟：</color><color=orange>ZONE 183。</color>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: <color=red>警告：应急电源装置失效，需要在以下区域的终端上手动重启：</color><color=orange>ZONE 183</color>。
